Invite Codes should actually
come with spare

00:43:29.710 --> 00:43:32.640
batteries as well.

00:43:32.640 --> 00:43:34.410
BRANDON BADGER: We could have a
partnership with the battery

00:43:34.410 --> 00:43:37.420
makers, right, and just sell
