college campus, we initially

00:45:54.080 --> 00:45:56.850
submitted works of art and one
person went around submitting

00:45:56.850 --> 00:45:59.410
just about everything.

00:45:59.410 --> 00:46:02.660
Some of the portals didn't get
approved, some of them did.

00:46:02.660 --> 00:46:06.000
So now we have these random
buildings that don't make

00:46:06.000 --> 00:46:06.880
sense as portals.

00:46:06.880 --> 00:46:14.310
Is there are going to be some
process to suggest portals

00:46:14.310 --> 00:46:15.600
