where you can't walk
five feet without

00:46:22.620 --> 00:46:23.510
tripping over a portal.

00:46:23.510 --> 00:46:23.970
BRANDON BADGER: Yeah.

00:46:23.970 --> 00:46:26.000
So the one complaint is the
portals aren't getting

00:46:26.000 --> 00:46:27.580
approved and added
fast enough.

00:46:27.580 --> 00:46:30.850
The other complaint is when
there's bad quality and things

00:46:30.850 --> 00:46:33.010
are getting approved that
shouldn't be approved.

00:46:33.010 --> 00:46:35.800
There is a tool in the game now
where you can report what

00:46:35.800 --> 00:46:37.190
you think is a bad portal.

00:46:37.190 --> 00:46:40.490
If you go into the Portal Info
View and you click on the

00:46:40.490 --> 00:46:42.880
photo, and you can report it,
and then that goes to one of

00:46:42.880 --> 00:46:44.830
our operators who can review
that and remove it.

00:46:44.830 --> 00:46:47.580
It's still a slow process, but
I can promise that it's

00:46:47.580 --> 00:46:48.770
something that will improve
and speed up.

