BRANDON BADGER: I think right
now, just flag it just in

00:46:59.100 --> 00:47:00.450
general as either a bad
description or a bad portal.

00:47:00.450 --> 00:47:03.000
AUDIENCE: My other question
is, what are the plans for

00:47:03.000 --> 00:47:04.650
Level Nine and above?

