debating that internally.

00:47:06.610 --> 00:47:08.930
We don't want to turn it into
a rat race where we go to

00:47:08.930 --> 00:47:13.430
Level 128, but we're trying to
think of other ways where we

00:47:13.430 --> 00:47:16.500
can have progression.

00:47:16.500 --> 00:47:17.555
We're thinking about it.

